node.text: The video that got my Tik Tok account with 800k followers deleted. I don’t waste any of my time there now 😀

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by WHISTLINDIESEL on July 27, 2021 tagging @d_bertrand850. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and outdoors.

node.text: Enjoy your minty clean $45k second gen @d_bertrand850 !! Cleanest one you’ll find especially with the super reliable Cummings motor. It rolls coal and I charged $45k because it’s a second gen with a sport bumper on it. Super valuable. One of the most valuable trucks out there. Super underrated. Everyone loves second gens so I charged $45k and that was a steal too. It didn’t even have rust on the roof yet.

node.text: 75% complete. 1% lift setting. People were flipping out saying I was running a lottery even though the “prize” has no value whatsoever so I made some changes. I will still be inviting 5 people to bring a friend to enjoy a weekend with me. If you participated don’t worry my offer still stands!

node.text: EDIT: SOLD. 800hp Twin Turbo 24v Cummins and a free 2nd Gen with it. Wheels are 22x14 American forces I believe. Motor starts and runs perfectly. Trans is shot. This is mostly for the motor/wheels. Rest of the truck will have some good parts though. Make me an offer. Located near Nashville TN.

node.text: So like 700 sensitive people called the FDA and they’re so mad at me for no reason 😂😂😂 They called me threatening to take my plane and take me to court and everything over this video. I never realized plane enthusiasts were so sensitive. So what am I going to do about it? Well….. I’m about to upload that soon 💀 Enjoy you dimly witted anti brain plane enthusiasts that don’t want me to learn how to fly 👻

node.text: Got a bigger bank for my birthday that understands how the world actually works. It’s funny how it went from “You’ll never be anything” to “Money changed you” in just 128 weeks. Except my mindset didn’t relate with those people when I had nothing, and it still doesn’t relate today. I screenshotted that comment years ago so I could use it to push me to do better. And to remind everyone now that no matter where you’re at, or what you’re doing, people will hate you. You just have to use it as fuel! I’m 23 years behind schedule so back to work.
